short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Override the standard new tab page with a random unfinished artwork from the Metropolitan Museum of Art's online collection

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This chrome extension deals with the premier show of the new MET Breuer building. The works displayed in this exhibition are unfinished works by artists from all over the world. For one reason or another these works were left aside to be completed at a later date. Here's your chance to capture some of the most famous unfinished pieces throughout history. Developed and designed by Ying He.
